query:
SELECT vorgang.api_id, COUNT(rel_station_dokument.dok_id) as count FROM vorgang, station, rel_station_dokument
        WHERE vorgang.id = station.vorgang_id AND
        rel_station_dokument.stat_id = station.id AND
        rel_station_dokument.dok_id = ANY($1)
        GROUP BY vorgang.id ORDER BY count DESC;
